title: Watch: What Would 'Sultans Of Swing' Solo Sound Like If It Was Performed By 12 Different Guitar Legends [News]
text:
Posted 9 hours ago 0 
Guitarist Andre Antunes presented an interesting rendition of Dire Straits classic " Sultans of Swing ," sharing his take on what the solo part would sound like performed by 12 different guitar icons. 
You can check out the full list of guitarists plus the clip itself in the section below. 
1. Slash (Guns N' Roses)2. Brian May (Queen)3. Randy Rhoads (Ozzy Osbourne)4. Mark Knopfler (Dire Straits)5. Jonny Buckland (Coldplay)
